		{"id":"0ebd2ea6367d5bc1","type":"text","text":"## FEDERATION_MOBILE_MONEY_ACCOUNT\n\n- **id** `uuid` `pk`\n- **title** `varchar(50)` `not null`\n- **created_at** `date` `default` `now()` `not null`\n- **description** `text`\n- **coop_fed_id** `uuid` `fk` references cooperative_federation(id) `not null`\n- **service_provider** `enum` (orange_money, mvola, airtel_money)","x":-3480,"y":765,"width":625,"height":260,"color":"#0984e3"},
