		{"id":"41731976e3bb9148","type":"text","text":"## MEMBERSHIP_FEES\n\n- **id** `uuid` `pk`\n- **created_at** `timestamp` `default` `now()`\n- **payment_method** `enum` (cash, bank transfer, mobile payment)\n- **type** `enum` (monthly, yearly, one-time)\n- **membership_id** `uuid` `fk` references membership(id) `not null`\n- **description** `text` `not null`\n- **is_paid** `boolean` `not null` `default` `false`","x":423,"y":1612,"width":557,"height":300,"color":"#0984e3"},
